idea:

as above so below
tell me who are satans disciples
satan or lucifer
demons or caulcifer

did one convert
get raised to the heavens
a holy ghost
diplomat of host
well who sent him?

well could there be 
a underground trinity
devilsh being
with all eyes seeing
and praises greating
yet fester and bring internal bleeding
on our misoury feeding

those are who i am fleeing
seeking the heavinly king being
and say give me wisdom, vision, and sooth saying! 
solomon heaven praising!
cattle in my feilds grazing!
late summer blooms of feeling forever lazing!

for cold harsh winters - hell yeah i'm trading!
give me cold cash
instead of a warm heavens greeting



